page.text: Condition 3 - AM & PM Peak Hour Traffic Volumes (2013 Build with Site)
The posted speed limit on O’Kelly Chapel Road is 50 mph, use Figure 4C-4
Minimum Minor Street Approach Volume (1 Approach) must exceed 100 vph
with one entry lane or 150 vph with two or more entry lanes. Therefore, the
intersection does not meet the Peak Hour Warrant for this Condition in the AM
and PM Peak Hours – both approaches are single entry lanes.
Major Street Approach (Total of Both Approaches):
Therefore by inspection of Figure 4C-4 of the MUTCD 2009, using the threshold
lines as a guide, a traffic signal is not warranted based on the Peak Hour Warrant
Analysis for the 2013 build with site traffic (Condition 3) for either the AM and PM
